Brush Lee is the revolutionary auto-foaming toothbrush that cleans your teeth in 10 seconds!
Put it in your mouth;
One button, 10 seconds easier but cleaner! 
  The smooth foam from Brush Lee is easier to reach all surfaces of the tooth, which is a great improvement for tooth cleaning. With Brush Lee's U-shaped mouthpiece, every tooth can be cleaned in 10 seconds at the same time.  Auto-foaming, let us no longer squeeze toothpaste, so don't worry about toothpaste falling on clothes or the ground. We all know that cleaning toothpaste is troublesome, especially when the toothpaste is dry.  Brush Lee is a portable toothbrush with a toothpaste bin. You can keep your breath fresh when you are on a  short trip. Let it clean your teeth in 10 seconds and restore your shiny smile as soon as possible.   Why does Brush Lee achieve the function of auto-foaming? After almost one year trials and testing, finally Brush Lee comes out. Multiple functions with one button click, it’s really convenient while brushing, especially for kids and the elder.  How does it vibrate? Here is how the magic happens. After testing many types of motors, magnetic suspension sonic motor is our final choice. Such motors produce high frequency acoustic vibrations that create cavitation effects in the periodontal instance.  The sound energy transmitted by each bristles produces a cavitation effect, which effectively cleans the teeth. Wireless Charging  The body is equipped with the latest charging technology. The built-in wireless charging (Qi) module adopts ABS flame retardant material.   Waterproof  IPX7 waterproof, you can wash the whole body of the machine. No need to worry about any damage of the brush. Mouthpiece Most of toothbrush bristles currently sols on the market, both traditional and E- toothbrushes are nylon bristles. It cleans the teeth by a large amount of physical mechanical friction, but at the same time, it is easy to damage the enamel and cause bleeding gums.  However, we choose the medical grade liquid silicone for the bristle, which has excellent physiological inertia and chemical inertness. It is widely used in baby pacifiers and medical supplies. It is soft and comfortable without damaging the gums and enamel. It does not cause any foreign sensation in the mouth, so it’s the ideal toothbrush material.  As for the bristle design, we refer to The Bass Method of Brushing recommended by the American Dental Association. Accordingly, the bristle and the teeth are aligned at an angle of 45°, and with testing and trials, the combination of the shape, length, thickness and arrangement of various bristle is perfect to achieve the best effect.Now, there are 1244 bristles on one Brush Lee mouthpiece. On average, each tooth is cleaned by nearly 38 bristles with comprehensive vibration cleaning. Where is toothpaste? It is hard to imagine that Brush Lee as a fully automatic toothbrush would ask a user to squeeze toothpaste.  With Brush Lee, you don’t even need to squeeze your own toothpaste because it is already done for you at the touch of a button. Brush Lee uses specialized toothpaste liquid. Compared with regular paste toothpaste, the toothpaste liquid can achieve rapid and even bubbling that can collaborate perfectly with our brush. Bluetooth APP  Want to brush your teeth longer? Perhaps a more intense brush?  You can change the time and intensity of brushing by changing the personal preference settings in the Brush Lee App. Such datas, like the number of days the brush used and the amount of power of the toothbrush are shown on the app
Four choices of the foaming time: 2 seconds, 3 seconds, 4 seconds, and 5 seconds;
Five types of brushing time: 10 seconds, 15 seconds, 20 seconds, 30 seconds, and 60 seconds;
Four modes for selection: Neophyte mode, Sensitive mode, Cleaning mode, and Polishing mode.
 Compared with the traditional toothbrush, what makes Brush Lee different?  Brushing your teeth is a daily routine, but not every one takes it seriously. The average brushing time is 60 seconds, not 180 seconds which is often recommended by dentists. You would spend 131 days on brushing teeth through your whole life, and ninety percent of tooth and gum disease is caused by improper brushing. Brush Lee makes brushing less annoying. Some of us are so sick of brushing our teeth that we don't brush long enough, or our method is ineffective or inefficient, or even not brushing our teeth at all. For those who brush their teeth carefully for 180 seconds in both morning and evening, Brush Lee has the advantage of saving time and making brushing more enjoyable.  10 seconds is unbelievable? You should brush your teeth every time up to a total of 180 seconds. It only takes 10 seconds to use Brush Lee. There’re about 32 teeth on the mouth, which adds up to 96 teeth surfaces overall. On average, traditional toothbrushes only brush per tooth surface for 1.875 seconds . But Brush Lee cleans teeth surfaces from all-round, and achieves the efficient brushing in 10 seconds by the high frequency vibration. This is far more than the actual time your teeth were brushed for, and achieves a fast and effective brushing effect. We conducted product trial and research after the small-scale manufacturing, and based on that result we have tested and optimized almost all components of the product, such as the mouthpiece, motors, batteries and pumps.This 10-Seconds Fully Auto-Toothbrush is a brand-new device that needs more supporting. The product links together those of us who are interested in health and passionate about technology. And more importantly, we want to be recognized by everyone.  Timeline  Now we need your help to enter the final stage, complete the final mass production. RewardsA good product needs your help to be effective. The prototype and pre-production unit is funded by us. However, here comes a great opportunity. At present, we are facing high upfront costs related to the mold, certification, research, minimum amount of purchase, as well as the development of bluetooth modules and apps. We need your support!  Join Brush Lee’s Family We believe that kickstarter is a platform where offer opportunity for many like-minded entrepreneurs and developers to get support. We hope that people like us will recognize and support Brush Lee!
